frames.caption: Two individuals walk side by side on a rainy city street, their reflections visible in the puddles below. The woman wears a hooded coat, while the man dons a fedora and leather jacket, both appearing deep in thought.
frames.description: The scene captures a rainy day in an urban setting, with two people walking through a wet street. The atmosphere is somber and reflective, enhanced by the overcast sky and the sound of raindrops hitting the ground.

frames.caption: Two individuals walk side by side on a rainy city street, their heads bowed under the weight of the weather and their thoughts. The woman wears a long, dark coat with the hood up, while the man dons a fedora and a leather jacket. Raindrops create ripples in the puddles on the pavement, reflecting the somber mood.
frames.description: The scene takes place on a city street during a rainy day. The atmosphere is melancholic, with two people walking quietly through the rain, seemingly lost in thought. The urban setting is characterized by tall buildings and wet pavement.
